data.description: Basically new construction for under $250,000!  Literally every inch of the house from foundation to roof has been redone making this the perfect turnkey home, vacation spot or investment for you.  Easy access to downtown, but still on a quiet street.  Finishes include new LVP floors, easy-close cabinets, stainless appliances, etc.  High quality house without the high dollar price tag.  Come check it out today!  No showings until Friday June 4th.
